OL,3,CChristmas night-bus service sees 70%
OL,4,Cincrease
OL,6,FThe night-bus service from Translink
OL,7,Fover the Christmas period saw a 70%
OL,8,Fincrease compared to the previous year.
OL,10,FThe transport provider is now being
OL,11,Furged to continue with the service
OL,12,Fduring a 12-month pilot scheme, to
OL,13,Ftest the viability of a year-round
OL,14,Fnight-bus.
OL,16,F"On the four weekends in the run up to
OL,17,FChristmas, 30,000 people used the late
OL,18,Fnight bus and rail services," Ian
OL,19,FCampbell from Translink told UTV.
