OL,3,CChristmas night-bus service sees 70%
OL,4,Cincrease
OL,6,F"That represented an increase of
OL,7,Faround 70% on the previous year, which
OL,8,Fis a success whatever way you look at
OL,9,Fit.
OL,11,F"In the weekends in 2025 in the run up
OL,12,Fto Christmas, we did operate some
OL,13,Fadditional bus services across 12
OL,14,Fcorridors between 12 and 2 o'clock in
OL,15,Fthe morning on Belfast Metro.
OL,17,F"We also ran some additional late
OL,18,Fnight services on Ulsterbus to places
OL,19,Flike Newry, Dungannon, Ballyclare,
OL,20,FCrumlin and other towns and cities
OL,21,Facross the province."
