OL,3,CChristmas night-bus service sees 70%
OL,4,Cincrease
OL,6,FUsually after Christmas the night-
OL,7,Fbuses come to an end but this year on
OL,8,Fa number of routes they'll continue as
OL,9,Fpart of a 12-month pilot scheme.
OL,11,FBelfast Night Czar Michael Stewart
OL,12,Fsaid: "I talk about motivation and
OL,13,Fhabit, the motivation was to get these
OL,14,Fon board and now that we have it we
OL,15,Fhave to change people's habits to get
OL,16,Fback into the way of using them.
