OL,3,CChristmas night-bus service sees 70%
OL,4,Cincrease
OL,6,F"So basically people can travel at
OL,7,Fmidnight and 2am. now in the morning,
OL,8,Fwhereas before it would have been
OL,9,Fclosing, buses would have been
OL,10,Ffinished at 11:00 and 11:30.
OL,12,F"This isn't just about coming out for
OL,13,Fa late night pint, this is about staff
OL,14,Fgetting home later, people who are
OL,15,Fusing the city center as workers to
OL,16,Fget home later and obviously also
OL,17,Fanybody who's a reveler or a traveler
OL,18,Fthat they can go home later as well."
