OL,6,FGetting the pilot scheme in place took
OL,7,Fover a year and required funding from
OL,8,Fa series of Stormont departments and
OL,9,FBelfast City Council.
OL,11,FTranslink got an early indication of
OL,12,Fhow popular those services could be.
OL,14,FIan Campbell said: "7,000 people
OL,15,Factually use the additional bus
OL,16,Fservices which will now continue for
OL,17,Fthe next year.
