OL,6,F"On Metro, that means for the next
OL,7,Fyear, on Friday and Saturday nights,
OL,8,Fwe will be operating additional late
OL,9,Fnight bus services between 12 and 2
OL,10,Fo'clock on 12 corridors in the greater
OL,11,FBelfast area, and we'll also be
OL,12,Foperating additional late night Ulster
OL,13,Fbus services."
OL,15,FThe hospitality sector believe this
OL,16,Fwill be a popular service - the
OL,17,Ffigures in 12 months will dictate if
OL,18,Fthey were right.
